items.name: Weather_dashboard
items.description: The Weather Dashboard is an interactive web application that provides real-time weather information and a 7-day forecast for any city. Users can view current weather details, an interactive map, and a temperature trend graph. The app features a custom light green and dark green theme for a visually appealing interface.
